application_type_full: Prior Approval: Change of use - offices to dwellinghouses
description:
Prior Approval application in relation to the following considerations arising from the change of use of floors 1-4 and 6-12 of the building to residential use (C3) use class creating up to 150 residential units:  
a)	transport and highways impacts of the development
b)	contamination risks on the site; and
c)	flooding risks on the site.
decision_conditions:
REFUSE/RECYCLING DETAILS:  Further details of dedicated refuse / recycling enclosures shall be  submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority prior to the occupation of the development hereby approved and shall be maintained as such thereafter.

REASON:  To secure the necessary physical waste enclosures to support the development and to ensure that responsible waste management practices are adhered to.
